---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Contact · EireQuant" description="Get in touch about EireQuant — research, models, pipelines, and collaboration.">
  <h1>Contact</h1>

  <section class="panel">
    <p class="lead">
      I’m building EireQuant while juggling final year at uni, I would love to hear feedback based on the work so far and any advice is greatly appreciated.
      For discussions regarding roles, collaborations, or just want to swap notes on markets, models, or infrastructure,
      please contact me either on email or Linkedin.
    </p>

    <div class="grid two-col">
      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Primary</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <strong>Email:</strong>
            <a href="mailto:oisinmcalinden2@gmail.com">oisinmcalinden2@gmail.com</a>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>LinkedIn:</strong>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/oisin-mcalinden-3b6a8a2a4/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
              Connect / DM on LinkedIn
            </a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="hint">Fastest way to reach me is email. I typically reply within 24–48 hours.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2 class="card-title">Also find me</h2>
        <ul class="list">
          <li>
            <strong>GitHub:</strong>
            <a href="https://github.com/omcalin102" target="_blank" rel="noopener">omcalin102</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="hint">Front end code, for backend please email.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>Why reach out?</h2>
    <div class="grid two-col">

      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="hsmall">Partnerships & collaboration</h3>
        <p>
          Interested in integrating models, benchmarking, or pipelines? I’m happy to collaborate
          on research, infra, or content — from feature engineering ideas to evaluation harnesses
          and reporting.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="hsmall">Model questions</h3>
        <p>
          Questions about the current models, calibration, regimes, or the policy trace?
          I’m glad to walk through the card, the live pipeline, or the workstation (Sim) notes.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h3 class="hsmall">General feedback</h3>
        <p>
          See something that could be clearer, faster, or more useful? Feedback on the website,
          docs, or visualizations is very welcome.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="panel">
    <h2>What to include</h2>
    <ul class="list">
      <li>Your name and how to reach you.</li>
      <li>Topic (e.g., role, collaboration, model card question, site feedback).</li>
      <li>Any links or context that would help me prep before replying.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="hint">Short is great — I’ll follow up with specifics if needed.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead{color:#444;margin:.2rem 0 .8rem}
  .hsmall{font-size:1rem;margin:.1rem 0 .4rem}
</style>
